N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 350.2 - No fee for 4-h, f.f.a., junior fair or school department exhibits

State Regulations

No entry fee shall be charged for 4-H Club, F.F.A. and junior
fair exhibits entered for competition in their own classes, or for entries in
the school department. Notes
